notesStmt.note: This informal interaction between Erasmus students takes place in a private home in Spain. S1, a student from England, has invited the others to celebrate pancake day with her. First they talk about the tradition associated with pancake day, about cookery and cooks on TV, then about the Eurovision Song Contest and music.

equipment.p: Portable minidisc recorder with electret condenser stereo microphone
